data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!  BACK ON THE MARKET!   Make your appointment today to see Your Water front home!  This 5200 square home with 6 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms.  Wake up in the Master bedroom on the balcony over looking the pool on to the lake.  This home also has a gym,  game room,  so much space for your whole family!  The home can offer 2 in law suits.  Wood burning fireplace in the family room with a wet bar.  The home also has Solar panels. LOWER BILL!  The pool is all screened in the a pool sweep,  lots of space to entertain outside!  Then you also have a large back yard!  This also has a 4 car garage,  with a  large driveway!  Close to shopping,  30-45 minutes from downtown Tampa and the airport.  About 45 minutes from the beaches.  45 minutes to Disney Orlando.  Call and make your appointment today!  SELLER IS MOTIVATED!!!!
